  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/69a048255bf4abf5bb6ecf4558a8f4c1.avif?t=1755107519\" width=576 height=841 /></span><br><br>HOUSE is a horror adventure game where you play as a young girl exploring a dangerous house that's doing everything it can to kill you and your family. Race against time to change fate...or fall into darkness yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/1680e25620dbff75502361c580d1a1da.poster.avif?t=1755107519\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/1680e25620dbff75502361c580d1a1da.webm?t=1755107519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/1680e25620dbff75502361c580d1a1da.mp4?t=1755107519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/0fa834aa753b3d46b310db1d41c3dc5f.poster.avif?t=1755107519\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/0fa834aa753b3d46b310db1d41c3dc5f.webm?t=1755107519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/0fa834aa753b3d46b310db1d41c3dc5f.mp4?t=1755107519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a house that changes and reacts to your actions in real-time<br></li><li>Race against time to save your family and yourself<br></li><li>Multiple endings to discover <br></li><li>Befriend or behead your family<br></li><li>Experiment with the different items to try and survive<br></li><li>Challenging, non-linear gameplay<br></li><li>Uncover the dark secrets of a twisted family</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/211b50919e18e12c0e1374e45be9a757.poster.avif?t=1755107519\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/211b50919e18e12c0e1374e45be9a757.webm?t=1755107519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/211b50919e18e12c0e1374e45be9a757.mp4?t=1755107519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/61f0e762d31fee7dfae6ff224fe0b313.poster.avif?t=1755107519\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/61f0e762d31fee7dfae6ff224fe0b313.webm?t=1755107519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/61f0e762d31fee7dfae6ff224fe0b313.mp4?t=1755107519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/bc2fa1135a5c38acec2f6f8008eaafbf.poster.avif?t=1755107519\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444350/extras/bc2fa1135a5c38acec2f6f8008eaafbf.webm?t=1755107519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as